{"tid":2318772,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣","createTime":"2020-12-09T14:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T15:34:28.000Z","uid":199606,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7fa00711e62f77f5c1d06cef9fd94fbfb78bb3","tid":2318772,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"基本上係全方位都有壓力<br />\n屋企 事業 前途 朋友 健康 <br />\n個啲好無形嘅壓力隨處都在<br />\n但係又講唔出個重點係邊到俾到壓力<br />\n好想自閉收埋自己 連機都唔想打<br />\n平時幫人氹人就識<br />\n當個問題係自己到就好迷<br />\n我已經冇瞓過好教好耐 兩三個鐘就醒一次<br />\n每日都會係惡夢咁起返身<br />\n好想消失 好想靜下 好想好想...<br />\n好想返去食粒糖就會開心嘅年紀"},{"pid":"972fe2f4b7ba2cea7a05ae6e726390bc21f91a74","tid":2318772,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"有咩可以幫到你"},{"pid":"ed16a7e59315dbc10e5ebad213576d981808a017","tid":2318772,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"972fe2f4b7ba2cea7a05ae6e726390bc21f91a74","tid":2318772,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"有咩可以幫到你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:55:46.000Z","msg":"其實冇 日子都係要咁過 只係呻下<br />\nThanks bro"},{"pid":"5ed1b43ecddae75b709bb9eee950b03fd25ab6c5","tid":2318772,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"21a2c8cc869b60ac43e9da2639a93eea1f032394","tid":2318772,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"好想返去中學<br />\n大家玩下玩下又一日<br />\n好青春好勇悍好開心<br />\n係個小小事就開心一日嘅年紀<br />\n想做咩就做咩 唔駛諗身份 唔駛諗好多嘢<br />\n完全冇壓力 大家嬉鬧下又一日<br />\n間唔時又可以拍下拖<br />\n邊似依家"},{"pid":"74758e2eeb837817d81896c7ee178f7087d681d8","tid":2318772,"uid":290414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ce32d8e2a8b52329342fb1afc1185e94a9dc1e","tid":2318772,"uid":366256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202